Package gui

Package containing all graphical user interfaces.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DatabaseAccessGUI Super class for GUIs that need access to the entries in the database.
Matching3DGui Graphical user interface to configure / execute 3d algorithm
PSGMGui Simple GUI for choosing two database entries and then execute the matching algorithm.
SearchGUI Simple GUI to start similarity searches in the database.
 

Package gui Description

Package containing all graphical user interfaces.

  • Matching3DGui - for the matching of 3D objects. You have to configure the environment variable LD_LIBRARY_PATH first to use this gui. See README for more details.
  • PSGMGui - for the matching of 2D images. The name of the database is specified by the command line parameter.
  • SearchGUI - for image retrieval tests. The name of the database is specified by the command line parameter.
